---
import { Mail, Linkedin } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section class="pt-[4.8rem] px-6 pb-0">
  <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto mb-[2.6rem] text-center fade-in">
    <h2 class="text-[2.1rem] tracking-tight mb-[0.6rem] font-bold">Kind words</h2>
    <p class="text-[0.98rem] text-base-content/70 leading-[1.75]">
      Teammates and partners describing what it feels like to build products with
      Kunal day‑to‑day.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[980px] mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-[1.6rem] fade-in">
    
    <article class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] card-gradient">
      <div class="card-body p-6">
        <p class="text-[0.96rem] text-base-content leading-[1.8] mb-[1.1rem]">
          “Kunal turns ambiguous health problems into crisp design decisions. He keeps
          the room calm, even when stakes and timelines are high.”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-[0.8rem] text-[0.86rem]">
          <div class="avatar placeholder">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent text-primary-content rounded-full w-10">
              <span class="font-bold">PM</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="block font-medium">Product Manager</span>
            <span class="block text-base-content/60">eka.care</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)]">
      <div class="card-body p-6">
        <p class="text-[0.96rem] text-base-content leading-[1.8] mb-[1.1rem]">
          “Working with him feels like having a design lead and a facilitator in one
          person. The team ships faster because conversations are clear.”
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-[0.8rem] text-[0.86rem]">
          <div class="avatar placeholder">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-accent text-primary-content rounded-full w-10">
              <span class="font-bold">ENG</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="block font-medium">Engineering Lead</span>
            <span class="block text-base-content/60">Health platform</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

  </div>

  <div id="contact" class="max-w-[820px] mx-auto mt-[3.4rem] glass glass-card rounded-[var(--radius-xl)] overflow-hidden fade-in">
    <div class="card-body p-[2.4rem_2.1rem] text-center relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-[-40%] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_0_0,var(--color-accent),transparent_60%)] opacity-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
      
      <div class="relative z-10">
        <h3 class="text-[1.7rem] mb-[0.5rem] tracking-tight font-bold">Have a complex product problem?</h3>
        <p class="text-[0.96rem] text-base-content/70 max-w-[32rem] mx-auto mb-[1.6rem] leading-[1.7]">
          Kunal thrives where constraints are real and impact is measurable. Share a
          short brief and he’ll respond with potential next steps or questions.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-[0.9rem] flex-wrap">
          <a href="mailto:kunal@example.com" class="btn btn-primary gap-2 rounded-full shadow-md">
            <Mail size={16} />
            Email Kunal
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pub/dir/Kunal/Katre" class="btn btn-outline gap-2 rounded-full" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
            <Linkedin size={16} />
            Connect on LinkedIn
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
